8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Alli AI and Yoast SEO share a solid foundation of core features including Content Optimization. Where Alli AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Site Audit and Reporting, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Yoast SEO uniquely offers Ai Writing, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Alli AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Yoast SEO scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Yoast SEO comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Alli AI begins at $299/mo. Yoast SEO stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Alli AI requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
